# Phase 3.2 Worker Module Migration Plan

This plan details the implementation strategy to migrate the Worker module to a Hexagonal / Clean Architecture design pattern, while maintaining strict backward compatibility for all dependent modules (Booking, Payment, Review, Chat) and test suites.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Geospatial & populate queries compatibility:**
> Dependent collections (such as `Booking`) populate the `workerId` reference. To ensure no breaking changes in Mongoose populations and aggregate lookups, the new Mongoose schema will compile to the model name `'Worker'` and will be exposed through a proxy wrapper in [models/Worker.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/models/Worker.js).

