## Verification & Test Impact Strategy

### Automated Tests
*   Run the full test suite:
    ```bash
    npm run test
    ```
*   Assert all tests in `cleanAuth.test.js`, `bookingStateMachine.test.js`, and `paymentRedirect.test.js` pass with a 100% success rate.

### Manual Verification
*   Verify Nearby Search: Hit `GET /api/v1/workers/nearby?lng=80.9462&lat=26.8467&radius=10` and check recommendation score calculations.
*   Verify dashboard sync: Load `/api/v1/workers/:id/dashboard` and verify analytics payload metrics.
*   Verify KYC updates: Submit KYC status updates (`/approve`, `/reject`, `/block`) and confirm state updates match.
